# dGraph | written in GO | started 2015
opensource distributed graph database whith native support for graphQL and JSON
search engine + graphDB + guarentees of transactions
[ query language + query execution layer + storage layer + distribution layer ] all work together
evolve data-model naturally in graphDB layer
build graphsystems like twitter, dropbox, airbnb default goto
schemas are built as we need them

## Features
- create nodes and traverse nodes
- multilanguaeg capability, strings are stored as utf-8 encoding
- hey db give me the data in particular langiage only => add @lang dicrective to schema, comment@en comment@fr comment@zh ISO codes for languages
- low-latency high-throughput arbitrary connections
- if you want to serve knowledge graph, data representing informaion in graph like data-structures



